      >.`,
      },
      {
        title: 'Endocrine Society & Magazine',
        description: `The Endocrine Society in US, recently recorded a 
          <a
            href="https://www.endocrine.org/podcast/enp83-sedentary-time-and-physical-activity-effects-on-childhood-lipid-levels"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="text-blue-700 hover:underline"
            ><b>podcast</b> interview</a
