          <a
            href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1n85Kj7kjfU"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="text-blue-700 hover:underline"
            ><b>press</b> conference</a
          >
           at the ENDO 2024 congress in Boston, US. `,
      },
      {
        title: 'European Association for the Study of Obesity',
        description: `He was 
          <a
            href="https://easo.org/changing-the-way-we-measure-childhood-obesity-in-conversation-with-andrew-agbaje/"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="text-blue-700 hover:underline"
            >interviewed by the European Association for the Study of Obesity</a
