          >, published in <span class="font-bold italic">Circulation</span>. He had a 
          <a
            href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QVhTdHjSOQo"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="text-blue-700 hover:underline"
            >video discussion</a
          >
           of the Scientific Statement. He was an invited guest speaker to the largest mother and child center in Canada – CHU Sainte-Justine Mother and Child University Hospital Center, Canada in March 2023 to speak on the 
          <a
            href="https://www.chusj.org/Calendrier-salle-presse/calendrier/Evenements/CDR/2023/Conference-scientifique-du-vendredi-midi-2023(8)"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="text-blue-700 hover:underline italic"
            >determinants of carotid intima-media thickness and arterial stiffness in pediatrics</a
          >.`,
      },
      {
        title: 'Honorary Research Fellow',
        description: `He is an Honorary Research Fellow at the 
          <a
            href="https://medicine.exeter.ac.uk/phss/research/childrenshealth/"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="text-blue-700 hover:underline"
            >Children’s Health and Exercise Research Centre</a
          >
          (CHERC), Department of Public Health and Sports Sciences, Faculty of Health and Life Sciences, University of Exeter, Exeter, UK.`,
      },
    ]}
