            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="text-blue-700 hover:underline"
            >editorial board</a
          >
           of Arteriosclerosis, Thrombosis, and Vascular Biology (ATVB), and mentors early-career editorial board members. He also serves on the 
           <a
            href="https://journals.humankinetics.com/view/journals/pes/pes-overview.xml?tab_body=editorial-board"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="text-blue-700 hover:underline"
            >editorial board</a
          >
           of Pediatric Exercise Science journal.`,
      },
      {
