            class="text-blue-700 hover:underline"
            >Fellow of the European Society of Cardiology</a
          >
          (FESC) and an elected 
          <a
            href="https://professional.heart.org/en/professional-membership/fellow-of-aha"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="text-blue-700 hover:underline"
            >Fellow of the American Heart Association</a
          >
           (FAHA). These titles of honour, symbol of excellence and lifetime achievement recognizes his significant contribution to cardiovascular field in Europe and America.`,
